snippet.title: Observe
snippet.description:
This channel is partnered with the Emotional Intelligence Academy in the UK and Ekman Group certified.

https://www.eiagroup.com/observe
You can get large discounts on any course offered, including the Master's Degree.

The EIA was established with the aim to create the most compelling education institution for social science-based learning in the world. Using the academic rigor of a top-flight university, combined with real-world practical application, EIA has developed unique programs covering foundation skills all the way up to the Master's Degree level.

Please note that due to the nature of our current understanding of psychology and nonverbal communication, anything I say in relation to any nonverbal reads I provide rests under the pretense of an educated opinion. No analysis uploaded to YouTube should be or has been intended to be utilized as an official form of evidence.
